'''/etc/portage/mirrors''' is a file that is used to modify mirror behavior. It is mostly useful for defining a local mirror that can contain fetch-restricted packages, when using multiple Gentoo machines.

==Example==
{{Code|/etc/portage/mirrors|<pre>
# local private mirror used only by my company
local ftp://192.168.0.3/distfiles
</pre>}}

